  <script>
    function getAccordionShouldBeInitiallyOpen(initiallyExpanded) {
      if (typeof initiallyExpanded === 'boolean') {
        return initiallyExpanded;
      }

      var isSmallScreenSizeAndUp = function () {
        return window.innerWidth >= 576;
      }

      if (initiallyExpanded === 'mobileOnly') {
        return (!isSmallScreenSizeAndUp());
      }

      if (initiallyExpanded === 'desktopOnly') {
        return (isSmallScreenSizeAndUp());
      }

      return false;
    }
  </script>

  <script>
    function getAccordionShouldBeInitiallyOpen(initiallyExpanded) {
      if (typeof initiallyExpanded === 'boolean') {
        return initiallyExpanded;
      }

      var isSmallScreenSizeAndUp = function () {
        return window.innerWidth >= 576;
      }

      if (initiallyExpanded === 'mobileOnly') {
        return (!isSmallScreenSizeAndUp());
      }

      if (initiallyExpanded === 'desktopOnly') {
        return (isSmallScreenSizeAndUp());
      }

      return false;
    }
  </script>

  <script>
    function getAccordionShouldBeInitiallyOpen(initiallyExpanded) {
      if (typeof initiallyExpanded === 'boolean') {
        return initiallyExpanded;
      }

      var isSmallScreenSizeAndUp = function () {
        return window.innerWidth >= 576;
      }

      if (initiallyExpanded === 'mobileOnly') {
        return (!isSmallScreenSizeAndUp());
      }

      if (initiallyExpanded === 'desktopOnly') {
        return (isSmallScreenSizeAndUp());
      }

      return false;
    }
  </script>

  <script>
    function getAccordionShouldBeInitiallyOpen(initiallyExpanded) {
      if (typeof initiallyExpanded === 'boolean') {
        return initiallyExpanded;
      }

      var isSmallScreenSizeAndUp = function () {
        return window.innerWidth >= 576;
      }

      if (initiallyExpanded === 'mobileOnly') {
        return (!isSmallScreenSizeAndUp());
      }

      if (initiallyExpanded === 'desktopOnly') {
        return (isSmallScreenSizeAndUp());
      }

      return false;
    }
  </script>

  <script>
    function getAccordionShouldBeInitiallyOpen(initiallyExpanded) {
      if (typeof initiallyExpanded === 'boolean') {
        return initiallyExpanded;
      }

      var isSmallScreenSizeAndUp = function () {
        return window.innerWidth >= 576;
      }

      if (initiallyExpanded === 'mobileOnly') {
        return (!isSmallScreenSizeAndUp());
      }

      if (initiallyExpanded === 'desktopOnly') {
        return (isSmallScreenSizeAndUp());
      }

      return false;
    }
  </script>

anchor</div><div id="LoadableAlternativesSection"><div class="nb-accordion-container "><div>
  <script>
    function getAccordionShouldBeInitiallyOpen(initiallyExpanded) {
      if (typeof initiallyExpanded === 'boolean') {
        return initiallyExpanded;
      }

      var isSmallScreenSizeAndUp = function () {
        return window.innerWidth >= 576;
      }

      if (initiallyExpanded === 'mobileOnly') {
        return (!isSmallScreenSizeAndUp());
      }

      if (initiallyExpanded === 'desktopOnly') {
        return (isSmallScreenSizeAndUp());
      }

      return false;
    }
  </script>
</div><div class="nb-accordion-section-container nb-w-full nb-overflow-hidden  nb-accordion-section-container-medium-mode nb-mb-xs nb-shadow-static" index="0"><input type="checkbox" data-test-id="hidden-input" class="nb-accordion-input nb-absolute nb-opacity-0 nb-z-10 nb-accordion-input-desktop-only" id="nb-accordion-preview-alternatives-0" checked="" data-bordered="true"/><div>
  <script>
    (function() {
      const input = document.getElementById('nb-accordion-preview-alternatives-0');
      const correctlyTypedInitiallyExpanded = 'desktopOnly';

      input.checked = getAccordionShouldBeInitiallyOpen(correctlyTypedInitiallyExpanded);
      input.classList.remove('nb-accordion-input-mobile-only');
      input.classList.remove('nb-accordion-input-desktop-only');
    })();
  </script>
</div><label for="nb-accordion-preview-alternatives-0" class="nb-accordion-header nb-border-secondary-200 nb-accordion-section-heading nb-accordion-section-heading-medium-mode nb-border-b-0   <script>
    function getAccordionShouldBeInitiallyOpen(initiallyExpanded) {
      if (typeof initiallyExpanded === 'boolean') {
        return initiallyExpanded;
      }

      var isSmallScreenSizeAndUp = function () {
        return window.innerWidth >= 576;
      }

      if (initiallyExpanded === 'mobileOnly') {
        return (!isSmallScreenSizeAndUp());
      }

      if (initiallyExpanded === 'desktopOnly') {
        return (isSmallScreenSizeAndUp());
      }

      return false;
    }
  </script>
